#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&knetattach; is a wizard which makes it easier to integrate your network "
"resources with your &kde; Desktop."
msgstr ""
"<application>K‑mrežohvat</application> je čarobnjak koji olakšava "
"integrisanje mrežnih resursa sa radnom površi KDE‑a."

#. Tag: keyword
