#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

# skip-rule: t-desktop
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &knetattach; wizard, affectionately and hereafter known as the Network "
"Folder Wizard, allows easy addition and integration of various network "
"folders with your &kde; desktop. Please report any problems or feature "
"requests for it to the &kde; bugs website."
msgstr ""
"Čarobnjak <application>K‑mrežohvat</application>, iz milja zvan čarobnjakom "
"mrežnih fascikli, omogućava lako dodavanje i integrisanje mrežnih fascikli u "
"radnu površ KDE‑a. Molimo da prijavite bilo kakve probleme ili želje za "
"novim mogućnostima na KDE‑ov veb sajt za praćenje grešaka."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &knetattach;"
msgstr "Korišćenje <application>K‑mrežohvata</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As you will see in the screenshot below, the Network Folder Wizard "
#| "currently allows you to add four types of network folders: WebDav, &FTP;, "
#| "&Microsoft; &Windows; (Samba) network drives and SSH. Additionally you "
#| "can select a recent connection for the list box."
msgid ""
"As you will see in the screenshot below, the Network Folder Wizard currently "
"allows you to add four types of network folders: WebDav, &FTP;, &Microsoft; "
"&Windows; (&Samba;) network drives and SSH. Additionally you can select a "
"recent connection for the list box."
msgstr ""
"Kao što možete videti na donjem snimku ekrana, čarobnjak mrežnih fascikli "
"trenutno omogućava dodavanje četiri tipa mrežnih fascikli: WebDAV, FTP, "
"windows mrežne jedinice (Samba) i SSH. Za spisak takođe možete izabrati "
"nedavno ostvarenu vezu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &knetattach;"
msgstr "Evo snimka ekrana <application>K‑mrežohvata</application>:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:96 index.docbook:124 index.docbook:264 index.docbook:288
#: index.docbook:306 index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network Folder Wizard main window"
msgstr "Glavni prozor čarobnjaka mrežnih fascikli."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding network folders"
msgstr "Dodavanje mrežnih fascikli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Network folders show up in a special location of &konqueror; and &dolphin; "
"called a <emphasis>virtual folder</emphasis>. This virtual folder is "
"accessed by typing <userinput>remote:/</userinput> in the location bar or by "
"selecting <guilabel>Network</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel. You will then be able to see any folders which have been previously "
"added and you also will be able to use the wizard to add new ones."
msgstr ""
"Mrežne fascikle pojavljuju se na specijalnoj lokaciji u "
"<application>K‑osvajaču</application> i <application>Dolphinu</application>, "
"zvanoj <emphasis>virtuelna fascikla</emphasis>. Virtuelnoj fascikli pristupa "
"se unošenjem <userinput>remote:/</userinput> u traku lokacije ili izborom "
"<guilabel>Mreža</guilabel> sa panela <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>. Time ćete "
"dobiti pregled svih ranije dodatih fascikli, i moći ćete čarobnjakom da "
"dodate nove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "The virtual folder with the Network Folder wizard"
msgstr "Virtuelna fascikla sa čarobnjakom mrežnih fascikli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Speaking of wizards, the Network Folder Wizard aims at being very easy to "
"use. After opening the wizard you must choose the type of network folder you "
"would like to access. When you move on to the next screen you will just need "
"to fill in the requested information. The final step is entering your "
"username and login password for the network share you've chosen to access."
msgstr ""
"Čarobnjak mrežne fascikle je zamišljen kao vrlo lak za upotrebu. Posle "
"otvaranja čarobnjaka, morate izabrati tip mrežne fascikle kojoj biste hteli "
"da pristupite. Kad pređete na sledeći ekran, treba samo da popunite tražene "
"podatke. Krajnji korak je unošenje vašeg korisničkog imena i prijavne "
"lozinke za mrežno deljenje kojem želite da pristupate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Below is a list of the information needed by the wizard to create the "
#| "network folders. If an option is not available for a particular folder it "
#| "does not have to be entered. The Samba folders &eg; do not require a "
#| "<guilabel>Port</guilabel> entry."
msgid ""
"Below is a list of the information needed by the wizard to create the "
"network folders. If an option is not available for a particular folder it "
"does not have to be entered. The &Samba; folders &eg; do not require a "
"<guilabel>Port</guilabel> entry."
msgstr ""
"Dole je spisak podataka potrebnih čarobnjaku za stvaranje mrežnih fascikli. "
"Ako za datu fasciklu neka opcija nije raspoloživa, ne mora se unositi; npr. "
"Samba fascikle ne zahtevaju port."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name:"
msgstr "Ime:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where you give a name to the network connection. It is limited only "
"by your imagination (or alphabet)."
msgstr ""
"Ovde dajete ime mrežnoj vezi. Ograničeno je samo vašom maštom (i abecedom)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "User:"
msgstr "Korisnik:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the username that will be used to establish the connection."
msgstr "Korisničko ime pod kojim će se uspostaviti veza."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid "Server:"
msgstr "Server:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the address of the server you are attempting to add. It can be an IP "
"address or domain name."
msgstr ""
"Adresa servera koji pokušavate da dodate. To može biti IP adresa ili ime "
"domena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Port:"
msgstr "Port:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you enter the port number you wish to connect to. The defaults are "
"usually sufficient."
msgstr ""
"Broj porta na koji želite da se povežete. Podrazumevani je obično dovoljan."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Not available for &Microsoft; &Windows; (Samba) folders."
msgid "Not available for &Microsoft; &Windows; (&Samba;) folders."
msgstr "Nije raspoloživo za windows (Samba) fascikle."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder:"
msgstr "Fascikla:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "The path to the folder you wish to connect to should go here."
msgstr "Putanja do fascikle na koju želite da se povežete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding:"
msgstr "Kodiranje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the items in this list box to select an encoding for &FTP; and ssh "
"connections."
msgstr "Preko stavki na ovom spisku birate kodiranje za FTP i SSH veze."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create an icon for this remote folder"
msgstr "Napravi ikonicu za ovu udaljenu fasciklu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked an icon will be created allowing access through the "
"remote:/ virtual folder. If it is not checked, a connection will be possible "
"but it will not be accessible from remote:/."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ova kućica popunjena, biće stvorena ikonica za pristup kroz virtuelnu "
"fasciklu <literal>remote:/</literal>. Ako nije popunjena, veza će biti "
"moguća, ali neće biti dostupna iz <literal>remote:/</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Recent connection:</guilabel> option allows you to re-connect "
"to the last network mount point you connected to using the wizard whether an "
"icon is created or not."
msgstr ""
"Opcija <guilabel>Nedavne veze:</guilabel> dopušta vam ponovno povezivanje na "
"poslednju mrežnu tačku montiranja na koju ste se povezali koristeći "
"čarobnjak, bez obzira na to da li je stvorena ikonica za nju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use encryption"
msgstr "Šifruj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked the ability to make a secure connection will be enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ako je uključeno, biće omogućena sposobnost ostvarivanja bezbedne veze."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available only for WebDav folders."
msgstr "Raspoloživo samo za webDAV fascikle."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "&knetattach; Walkthrough"
msgstr "Prolazak kroz <application>K‑mrežohvat</application>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will be a quick walkthrough of the Network Folder Wizard. Don't blink "
"or you might miss it."
msgstr ""
"Sledi brzi prolazak kroz čarobnjak mrežnih fascikli. Ne trepćite, inače "
"biste ga mogli propustiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Below you see the main window of the Network Folder Wizard. It is here that "
"we choose what type of folder we want to add or connect to. For the purposes "
"of this walkthrough we will be using &FTP;. It contains most of the options "
"you will encounter while using the wizard."
msgstr ""
"Ispod vidite glavni prozor čarobnjaka mrežnih fascikli. U njemu se bira tip "
"fascikle za dodavanje ili povezivanje. U svrhu prolaska upotrebićemo FTP, "
"koji sadrži većinu opcija koje ćete sresti u čarobnjaku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of the &knetattach; main window"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana glavnog prozora <application>K‑mrežohvata</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"OK, so we (as in me) have chosen to add an &FTP; folder. Below you see an "
"example of the type of information you will need to add for your particular "
"&FTP; server. After filling it in we press <guibutton>Save &amp; Connect</"
"guibutton> and wait for the magic. Oh yes, if your server requires "
"validation of some kind you will be prompted at this point before being "
"allowed to connect."
msgstr ""
"Biramo, dakle, FTP fasciklu. Dole vidite primer podataka koje treba upisati "
"za dodavanje jednog određenog FTP servera. Posle popunjavanja, pritiskamo "
"<guibutton>Sačuvaj i poveži se</guibutton> i čekamo da se odradi posao. Ako "
"server traži nekakvu overu, bićete upitani za nju pre nego što se "
"povezivanje dopusti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot showing addition of &FTP; Folder using &knetattach;"
msgstr ""
"Snimak ekrana o dodavanju FTP fascikle <application>K‑mrežohvatom</"
"application>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So now we are all connected now and able to navigate our newly added share. "
"Joy!"
msgstr ""
"Sad kad smo povezani, možemo se baciti u šetnju kroz novododato deljenje. "
"Uživajte!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the connected &FTP; folder"
msgstr "Snimak ekrana povezane FTP fascikle."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get back to our network folders all that is necessary is typing "
"<action>remote:/</action> in the location bar of &konqueror; or &dolphin; or "
"select <guilabel>Network</guilabel> from the <guilabel>Places</guilabel> "
"panel."
msgstr ""
"Za povratak na mrežne fascikle, sve što treba je da upišete "
"<userinput>remote:/</userinput> u traku lokacije u <application>K‑osvajaču</"
"application> ili <application>Dolphinu</application>, ili izaberete "
"<guilabel>Mreža</guilabel> sa panela <guilabel>Mesta</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the remote:/ virtual folder with the added connection"
msgstr ""
"Snimak ekrana virtuelne fascikle <literal>remote:/</literal> sa dodatom "
"vezom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can even add new folders from the same location by using the "
"<guilabel>Add a Network Folder</guilabel> link. Well that brings us to the "
"end of our walkthrough (told you it would be quick). I wish you the best of "
"luck in your own network folder adventures ;-)"
msgstr ""
"Sa iste lokacije takođe možete dodavati nove fascikle putem veze "
"<guilabel>Dodaj mrežnu fasciklu</guilabel>. Ovim smo završili prolazak "
"(rekosmo da će biti kratak). Sve najbolje u vašim budućim avanturama kroz "
"mrežne fascikle!"

